review: I got to know about Dr. Shreedevi through one of my friends. She is really friendly, makes you feel comfortable, pays attention and is extra careful when you're anxious. The consultation process is also pretty convenient as she herself does the scan so you don't have to run between clinic and diagnostic centre for routine scans/sonography .
